 
 +========================================+
 |  Mainline Linux kernel for H3 devices  |
 +========================================+

This kernel tree is based on mainline kernel 4.9.0, plus various patches primarily intended for Orange Pi PC, Orange Pi One, and Orange Pi Zero. Please feel free to modify the appropriate .dts files and port it to other H3-based boards.

WHAT WORKS:

- Ethernet driver
- USB host controllers
- CPU frequency and voltage scaling (cpufreq)
- Thermal regulation (CPU-based cooling)
- HDMI driver
- USB OTG port (for USB gadgets)


TODO:

- SPI flash support
- Audio support
- Video decoding support

